rows.label: qev085301_MSG0001
rows.name: Friends have company![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0002
rows.name: Hey there, Irina. You helping out Elma's team today?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0003
rows.name: Just finished up, actually.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0004
rows.name: Well, don't leave yet. I got a job that can use all of ya.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0005
rows.name: What, that tough of a mission?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0006
rows.name: I don't know if "tough" is the word, exactly...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0007
rows.name:
Basically, we got an SOS from a Prospector team,
and I want you to go follow up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0008
rows.name: It's from Kiefer and Leland Cole.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_JNK0010
rows.name: Assume

rows.label: qev085301_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask if they are father and son.

rows.label: qev085301_JNK0020
rows.name: Guess

rows.label: qev085301_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask if they're brothers.

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0009
rows.name: Makes sense. Same last name, similar face.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0010
rows.name:
Yup. They're a bit of an odd couple, but...
Well, you'll see what I mean.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0011
rows.name: Hmm, maybe. Same last name, similar face.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0012
rows.name: But I don't know, they seem more like father and son to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0013
rows.name:
That's right, Lin. Father and son,
and a bit of an odd couple, honestly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0014
rows.name:
You say they're Prospectors;
I assume they were out on a mineral survey?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0015
rows.name: Yeah, they're both geologists or somethin'.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0016
rows.name:
The kid followed in his old man's footsteps,
works as his assistant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0017
rows.name: Okay, we're on it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0018
rows.name: Let's get moving. Send us the data.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085301_MSG0019
rows.name: Great, will do.[ST:wait ]
